      "element_type": "speaker_note",
      "element_id": "slide_27_notes",
      "source_text": "Salaries/ wages/pension contributions\u000b(but not benefits such as healthcare, cars etc.)\nRegulatory expenses generally paid to government agencies\nDividends paid to shareholders\nCompensation/fines/warranty claims etc., paid to customers\nDepreciation charges applied to fixed assets\nTaxes paid on the organisations operations such as Business Rates/ National Insurance etc.",
